I think there comes a time when your livejournal becomes so much more than it was before. I never really knew that when I first signed up for this account that I would actually be using it. In fact, this LJ has kept me content at times, happy in others, frustrated sometimes, and have even helped me thereupeutically. It's helped me grow. And I just started posting this January of 2005. Imagine what wonders it would do for me in a years time, or even 2 or maybe even 5?
